description: Dramatic 2-Story Condo in Colony Square, the Heart of Midtown!  Discover the epitome of urban living in this stunning 1,500 Sq Ft condo located in vibrant Colony House. This residence boasts 2-story windows that offer a breathtaking view of the beautiful garden patio of Saints + Council and the exciting city-scape of Midtown.  The open floor plan downstairs features hardwood floors and offers ample space for entertaining. The living room seamlessly flows into the dining area, which then opens up to great kitchen for all your culinary needs. A convenient powder room for guests is also available downstairs, along with extra storage space under the stairwell. The washer and dryer are placed in a closet next to the kitchen for easy access.  Upstairs, you will find two large, carpeted bedrooms and two bathrooms. The master bathroom has been updated with tiles, a new walk-in shower, and a spacious walk-in closet. Additionally, the loft on the second floor presents a versatile space that can serve as an office or accommodate a Murphy bed.  This home can be sold fully furnished.  The Colony House Condo is pet-friendly and is surrounded by numerous parks, making it an ideal choice for pet owners.  Living in Colony Square means enjoying the best of the urban "live-work-play" lifestyle. With a fantastic selection of restaurants and a food court right at your doorstep, you'll find little need to cook. MARTA is just one block away, providing quick access to the airport. Additionally, you are within walking distance of Piedmont Park, the Beltline, Botanical Gardens, Alliance Theater, Museum, Symphony, Whole Foods, and yoga classes.  Embrace the luxurious urban living experience that Colony Square has to offer. This condo is not just a home, but a gateway to a vibrant, dynamic lifestyle.
